Multi-Peptide Lash and Brow Serum
fields.description:
The Ordinary Multi-Peptide Lash and Brow Serum is a lightweight, non-greasy formula designed to promote thicker, fuller, and healthier-looking lashes and brows. This serum combines 11 active ingredients, including peptide complexes and natural extracts, to nourish and protect lashes and brows. Key ingredients like Myristoyl Pentapeptide-17, Biotinoyl Tripeptide-1, and Caffeine work to enhance the density and overall appearance of your lashes and brows, showing visible improvements in as little as four weeks with consistent, twice-daily use.

This vegan and cruelty-free formula is free of alcohol, oil, and silicone, making it suitable for all skin types. It’s recommended for use both in the morning and evening after cleansing the application area.

Aveeno Daily Moisturizing Body Lotion with Soothing Oat
fields.description: Aveeno Daily Moisturizing Body Lotion with Soothing Oat is designed to provide intense hydration for dry and sensitive skin. Formulated with soothing prebiotic oat, this fragrance-free lotion is clinically proven to moisturize and lock in moisture for 24 hours. Its fast-absorbing, non-greasy formula leaves your skin feeling soft, smooth, and healthy-looking. Free of parabens and dyes, it’s gentle enough for daily use and helps restore the skin’s natural moisture barrier, making it a perfect choice for those with sensitive skin. Dermatologist-recommended for over 70 years, this lotion is an ideal solution for long-lasting hydration.

fields.name: Eucerin Intensive Repair Lotion White/Red 625ml
fields.description: Eucerin Intensive Repair Body Lotion is specifically formulated to provide deep hydration for very dry, flaky skin. With its unique 3-dimensional system, it moisturizes, exfoliates, and conditions the skin to restore its natural radiance. Enriched with Alpha Hydroxy and Natural Moisturizing Factors, this lotion helps to lock in moisture and support the skin's natural exfoliation process, leaving it soft and smooth. Fragrance-free, dye-free, and paraben-free, it is gentle enough for daily use, even for those with sensitive skin. Dermatologist-recommended, this lotion offers 24-hour hydration, making it an ideal choice for replenishing dry skin all day long.

fields.name: Glycolic Acid 7% Exfoliating Toner
fields.description: This exfoliating toner contains 7% glycolic acid, a well-known alpha-hydroxy acid (AHA) that helps improve skin texture and radiance. It also includes aloe vera and ginseng to soothe and balance the skin, and is formulated to reduce the appearance of uneven tone and fine lines. Designed for daily use, it smooths the skin and boosts luminosity. Ideal for evening use, it’s not recommended for sensitive or compromised skin. Always use sun protection when using this product as it can increase sensitivity to UV rays

fields.name: The Ordinary AHA 30% + BHA 2% Peeling Solution 30ml
fields.description: This powerful exfoliating peel combines 30% alpha-hydroxy acids (AHA) and 2% beta-hydroxy acid (BHA) to deeply exfoliate, helping improve skin clarity, texture, and the appearance of blemishes. The AHA works on the surface of the skin to remove dead cells, while the BHA penetrates deeper to unclog pores. This intense treatment is best suited for experienced users looking for a high-strength exfoliation but should be used with caution on sensitive skin. As it increases sun sensitivity, always follow up with sunscreen.

fields.name: The Ordinary Salicylic Acid 2% Solution 30ml
fields.description: Formulated with 2% salicylic acid, this serum helps to clear and exfoliate the inside walls of pores to fight acne and improve skin clarity. It’s ideal for targeting blemishes and uneven skin texture. The lightweight formula is suitable for oily and acne-prone skin types. As with all exfoliants, sun protection is recommended during use.

fields.name: The Ordinary Lactic Acid 10% + HA 30ml
fields.description: This serum combines 10% lactic acid, an AHA, with hyaluronic acid (HA) to gently exfoliate the skin while maintaining hydration. The lactic acid helps to improve texture and reduce the appearance of fine lines, while HA provides moisture. It’s suitable for most skin types, particularly those with dry or sensitive skin. Like other acid-based treatments, it should be used with caution and followed by sun protection

fields.name: Mixa Shea Ultra Soft Nährende Creme
fields.description: The Mixa Shea Ultra Soft Nährende Creme (400ml) is a deeply nourishing cream formulated with 20% plant-based glycerin and shea butter, making it ideal for very dry skin. It provides intense hydration for up to 48 hours and is suitable for the whole family, including babies, children, and adults. The cream has a rich texture that absorbs quickly without leaving a greasy residue, and it is designed to soothe and protect the skin from dryness, rough patches, and tightness. This multipurpose cream can be used on the face, body, and hands, making it a versatile option for maintaining soft, moisturized skin.

fields.name: The Mixa Urea Cica Repair+ Skin Renewing Cream
fields.description: The Mixa Urea Cica Repair+ Skin Renewing Cream is designed for dry, rough, and uneven skin. It contains 10% urea, which provides deep hydration and gentle exfoliation, and niacinamide, which soothes the skin and helps repair its barrier. This cream is formulated for use on the face, body, and hands, making it highly versatile. It works by gently removing dead skin cells while stimulating skin renewal, leaving skin visibly smoother and softer from the first application. The non-greasy formula absorbs quickly, providing long-lasting hydration and relief from skin irritation​

fields.name: Retinol Advanced Firming Cream (No Added Fragrance)
fields.description:
The Advanced Clinicals Retinol Advanced Firming Cream (No Added Fragrance) is formulated to help reduce visible signs of aging such as wrinkles, fine lines, and uneven skin tone. It contains retinol, which promotes skin renewal, along with other natural ingredients like green tea, chamomile, and aloe vera to soothe and hydrate the skin. This dermatologist and allergy-tested cream is non-irritating and designed to replenish the skin's moisture barrier, leaving it firmer and more radiant.

The cream is suitable for all skin types and can be applied to the face, neck, and body. It absorbs quickly, providing long-lasting moisture without being greasy. For best results, it's recommended to apply daily on cleansed skin

fields.name: Vitamin C Brightening Body Cream
fields.description:
The Advanced Clinicals Vitamin C Brightening Body Cream is designed to hydrate, brighten, and improve the appearance of dull and uneven skin. Formulated with potent ingredients like Vitamin C, Vitamin E, Aloe Vera, and Green Tea, it works to enhance skin radiance, reduce dark spots, and improve overall skin tone. Coconut oil in the formula helps deeply moisturize, while Jojoba oil locks in moisture for lasting hydration.

This non-greasy, fast-absorbing cream is suitable for daily use and can be applied to the face, neck, and body. It is ideal for addressing concerns like scars, stretch marks, sun damage, and hyperpigmentation, helping to reveal smoother, firmer skin

fields.name: Medix 5.5 Collagen + Peptides Treatment Cream
fields.description:
Medix 5.5 Collagen + Peptides Treatment Cream is designed to target signs of aging such as sagging skin, wrinkles, and fine lines. It combines collagen with peptides to help boost skin elasticity, firmness, and promote collagen production. This cream hydrates and nourishes the skin, leaving it soft, smooth, and visibly plumper.

Formulated with additional ingredients like shea butter, aloe vera, and Vitamin E, it helps to soothe and moisturize the skin while improving texture and tone. The cream is gentle enough for use on both the face and body, and is suitable for all skin types, including sensitive and dry skin. It is free from parabens, sulfates, and mineral oil, ensuring a non-greasy, pH-balanced experience

fields.name: Medix 5.5 Hyaluronic Acid + Cica Extract
fields.description:
The Medix 5.5 Hyaluronic Acid + Cica Extract Body Treatment Cream is a highly effective moisturizer designed to deeply hydrate and soothe dry, dehydrated skin. It combines Hyaluronic Acid, known for its ability to retain moisture and improve skin elasticity, with Cica (Centella Asiatica) Extract, which promotes healing and reduces inflammation. This cream also contains Apple Extract and Squalane to further enhance moisture retention, leaving your skin feeling soft, smooth, and revitalized.

It’s formulated to be suitable for all skin types and can be used daily to restore the skin’s hydration and protect it from environmental damage. The cream is also dermatologist-tested, cruelty-free, and free from parabens, formaldehyde, and other harmful ingredients.

This cream is ideal for improving the appearance of dry, flaky, or rough skin, providing a smoother and more supple skin texture over time

fields.name: Medix 5.5 Argan Oil + Vitamin E
fields.description:
The Medix 5.5 Argan Oil + Vitamin E Dryness Relief Body Cream is formulated to deeply hydrate and restore dry, uneven skin. Argan oil, known for its high content of nourishing unsaturated fatty acids and vitamin E, helps to improve skin elasticity and texture. The cream also includes Green Coffee Extract to tone and revitalize the skin, targeting dimpled or sagging areas, and promoting a smoother, more supple skin tone.

This fast-absorbing, non-greasy formula is pH-balanced and free from parabens, formaldehyde, and mineral oils, making it suitable for daily use. It also contains Shea Butter and Aloe Vera for added moisture and soothing properties. Ideal for addressing dryness and uneven skin tone, this cream works well for those dealing with fine lines, sagging skin, or areas prone to "orange peel" texture

fields.name: Haruharu Wonder Centella Phyto & 5 Peptide Concentrate Cream 30ML
fields.description:
The Haruharu Wonder Centella Phyto & 5 Peptide Concentrate Cream is an all-in-one vegan moisturizer designed to address signs of aging. It contains a 5 Peptide Complex, which helps improve skin firmness, reduces the appearance of fine lines, and enhances skin elasticity. Additionally, it includes Centella Asiatica Extract (Cica), known for its soothing properties, and Hydrolyzed Soy Protein and Adenosine to moisturize and promote collagen production.

This cream is further enriched with Squalane and Caffeine, which brighten the skin and reduce puffiness, leaving your complexion radiant and dewy. The formula is free from silicones, alcohol, and artificial fragrances, making it suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin. It's perfect for those seeking anti-aging, soothing, and brightening benefits in one product

fields.name: SOME BY MI - AHA,BHA,PHA 30DAYS MIRACLE ACNE CLEAR FOAM 100ml
fields.description: The SOME BY MI AHA, BHA, PHA 30 Days Miracle Acne Clear Foam is a daily acne-clearing cleanser that targets excess sebum and dead skin cells. It contains AHA, BHA, and PHA to exfoliate and deep-clean pores, while Tea Tree Leaf Water and Centella Asiatica soothe and heal the skin. This dermatologist-tested formula is ideal for acne-prone skin, helping to reduce blemishes and improve overall skin texture in as little as 30 days.

fields.name: COSRX - LOW PH GOOD MORNING GEL CLEANSER
fields.description:
The COSRX Low pH Good Morning Gel Cleanser is a gentle, pH-balanced cleanser designed for daily use. It effectively removes impurities and excess sebum without stripping the skin of its natural moisture, thanks to its mildly acidic formula (pH of around 5.3). This helps maintain your skin's moisture barrier, keeping it hydrated and balanced.

The key ingredients include Betaine Salicylate (BHA) and Tea Tree Oil, which help exfoliate dead skin cells, soothe irritation, and clear pores. It also contains a blend of botanical extracts like Saccharomyces Ferment and Evening Primrose Extract, which aid in soothing and protecting the skin.

This cleanser is ideal for those with sensitive, oily, or acne-prone skin and can be used both in the morning and at night

fields.name: COSRX - SALICYLIC ACID DAILY CLEANSER 150ml
fields.description:
The COSRX Salicylic Acid Daily Gentle Cleanser is a foaming face wash formulated with 0.5% salicylic acid, ideal for acne-prone and oily skin. This cleanser helps to exfoliate dead skin cells, unclog pores, and reduce excess sebum, preventing breakouts and blackheads. The inclusion of tea tree oil and willow bark water offers additional soothing and antibacterial benefits, making it effective for calming irritated skin while promoting a clear complexion.

It is designed to be gentle enough for daily use without stripping the skin of moisture, leaving it soft and smooth. Suitable for all skin types, especially those dealing with blemishes and oiliness, it provides deep cleansing and exfoliation while maintaining skin hydration.

fields.name: SKIN 1004 CENTELLA AMPOULE FOAM(125ml)
fields.description: Centella Ampoule Foam (125ml): This gentle foaming cleanser contains Centella Asiatica to calm and soothe irritated skin while providing deep cleansing. It removes dirt and impurities without stripping the skin of moisture, leaving it refreshed and hydrated. Ideal for sensitive and acne-prone skin, it helps maintain a clear complexion with its anti-inflammatory properties​.

fields.name: ANUA Heartleaf Pore Control Cleansing Oil
fields.description: This lightweight cleansing oil is formulated with Heartleaf Extract, which has anti-inflammatory and soothing properties, making it perfect for sensitive and acne-prone skin. It effectively removes makeup, sunscreen, and excess oil while controlling sebum production, helping to prevent breakouts. It’s an ideal first step in a double cleansing routine​.

fields.name: ANUA Heartleaf 70% Intense Calming Cream (50ml)
fields.description: This calming cream contains 70% Heartleaf Extract along with Ceramide and Panthenol to soothe and hydrate sensitive skin. It helps to maintain the skin’s moisture barrier, reduce irritation, and provides long-lasting hydration. Its lightweight, non-greasy texture makes it suitable for all skin types, especially for those with sensitive or dry skin.

fields.name: ANUA Heartleaf Quercetinol Pore Deep Cleansing Foam
fields.description: This cleansing foam is designed to deeply cleanse and gently exfoliate the skin using 3,000ppm Heartleaf powder. It’s perfect for oily and combination skin types, as it helps to clear pores and reduce sebum production. Additionally, the formula contains Quercetinol and Hyaluronic Acid, which soothe, hydrate, and leave the skin feeling refreshed and balanced after cleansing. It is gentle enough for daily use, even for sensitive skin​.

fields.name: CeraVe Hydrating Cleanser (236ml)
fields.description: This cleanser is formulated to cleanse and hydrate the skin without disrupting the skin’s natural moisture barrier. It contains hyaluronic acid, ceramides, and glycerin, which work together to provide moisture, making it ideal for dry and sensitive skin. Its non-foaming formula is designed to be gentle while effectively removing dirt and makeup, leaving the skin soft and nourished​

fields.name: Micro Ingredients Multi Collagen Protein Powder, 1Lb(454 g)
fields.description: This unflavored, hydrolyzed multi-collagen peptide powder includes five types of collagen (I, II, III, V, X) along with Hyaluronic Acid, Biotin, and Vitamin C to support joint, skin, hair, and nail health. It's ideal for keto and paleo-friendly diets, dissolving easily in hot or cold liquids. Non-GMO and free from additives, it helps replenish the body's collagen for a youthful glow and stronger joints​.

fields.name: Medicube - Collagen Jelly Cream (110ml)
fields.description: This Niacinamide-infused collagen jelly cream offers anti-aging benefits, promoting skin firmness and elasticity. The unique jelly texture contains freeze-dried hydrolyzed collagen to improve sagging and dull skin. It's formulated to give a 'glass skin' glow, restoring hydration and enhancing skin texture

fields.name: Glowy N Glassy Ultra Barrier Repairing Cream

fields.name: JUMISO SNAIL MUCIN 95 + PEPTIDE ESSENCE 140ML
fields.description: This essence is formulated with 95% snail mucin, known for its hydrating and skin-repairing properties, and 5 peptides, which help boost collagen production and reduce signs of aging. fields.name: Mary&May] Vegan Blackberry Complex Cream Essence

fields.name: Hada labo - GOKUJYUN PREMIUM LOTION 170ML

fields.name: Beauty Of Joseon GINSENG ESSENCE WATER

fields.name: MIXSOON SOONDY CENTELLA ASIATICA ESSENCE

fields.name: Paula’s Choice 2% BHA Liquid Exfoliant 118ML

fields.name: ANUA BHA 2% GENTLE EXFOLIATING TONER 150ML

The addition of Tea Tree Leaf Extract helps reduce redness, regulate sebum production, and soothe irritated skin, making it suitable for acne-prone and sensitive skin. Its lightweight, watery texture ensures it applies smoothly without irritation, leaving skin clearer, smoother, and more radiant

fields.name: HARUHARU BLACK RICE BAKUCHIOL EYE CREAM 20ML
